cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on video recognition and introduces a new deep neural network architecture for multi-label and multi-task learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions a semantic taxonomy that encompasses the recognition of multiple semantic aspects in the dynamic scene, which suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
